SUMMARY:ENRG HTX - June 2026
DTSTAMP:20260618T030749Z
DTSTART:20260619T083000Z
DESCRIPTION:Register here: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/enrg-htx-june-2026-
	tickets-1990513456331 \nENRG (Entrepreneurial Networking Resource Group) i
	s a community for entrepreneurs with 10-250 employees running on EOS or EO
	S Curious. \n\n\n\n\nENRG (pronounced energy) is here to stay in Houston! 
	\nErick Garcia\, Lesa A Skipper and Craig Ceccanti are teaming up to build
	 the Houston ENRG Chapter and we could not be more excited to invite entre
	preneurs running on EOS or EOS Curious to this collaborative room! Join us
	 on June 19th at 8:30am at the Ion District (Downstairs 028) for the first
	 meeting! \nWhat is ENRG?\nThe vision is to establish an ENRG (Entrepreneu
	rial Networking Resource Group) in Houston for entrepreneurs with 10-250 e
	mployees. This is a free EOS Worldwide aligned community for entrepreneurs
	 led by one EOS Implementer and one Integrator. \nEach monthly meeting inc
	ludes:\n– Practical training on an EOS tools\n– Peer-to-peer issue solving
	\n– Valuable networking\n– Content that helps move the needle on your busi
	ness\n– Exposure to Subject Matter Experts\nNo sales pitches here though\,
	 we’re here to help all tides rise! \nThis is WHERE entrepreneurs find the
	 WHOs and the HOWs to move their business forward.\n\nhttps://iondistrict.
	com/event/enrg-htx-june-2026/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/enrg-htx-june-2026/
LOCATION:Ion – Conference Room 028\, 4201 Main St.\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\,
	 United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
